phrases: Sometimes, a girl cannot stop loving, even if she knows better.
She will find a love she wants to believe in,
no matter how painful it is.
A girl always wants to believe that love conquers all.
If there is anyone who tries to get in their way...
In the name of the moon, Sailor Moon will punish them!
Gomen ne sunao ja nakute yume no naka nara ieru
Shikou kairo wa short sunzen i am about to sugu aitai yo
Nakitakunaru you na moonlight denwa mo dekinai midnight
Datte junjou dou shiyou heart wa mangekyou
Seiza no matataki kazoe uranau koi no yukue
Onaji kuni ni umareta no miracle romance
I do not look like a super heroine, but I am!
As you know, I transform myself by using a peculiar brooch
I am the sailor warrior of love and justice, Sailor Moon!
And my friends are the smart and sweet Ami Mizuno,
and a slightly quick-tempered psychic girl, Rei Hino.
Both of them are so dependable, I feel like I will fall behind.
But anyway, I just have to do my best!
Say, Naru, I think it would be better if you forget about him.
No matter how bad he is, I still love him.
Usagi, you have someone you love, do not you?
Then, you should understand how I feel.
Why did the Black Crystal respond to that girl?
Was that the energy of love?
I love him with all my heart, so...
Sailor Moon knew that girl's name.
That girl must know Sailor Moon's true identity.
So, that is the Black Crystal that is supposed to reveal
the location of the Silver Crystal.
The Black Crystal is responding again.
Could the Silver Crystal be something inside a human body?
The Silver Crystal is not inside this girl.
Masato Sanjoin is only a disguise.
I do not want to lie to you anymore.
Please just stay there and listen.
Thanks to you, I have learned what love is for the first time.
In the evil organization I have been a part of, there is no love.
We betray each other and kill each other for our own gain.
I thought that was normal, but your love opened my eyes.
Now, I am thinking that I would like to join Sailor Moon
to fight against the evil organization.
If you know anything about Sailor Moon, please tell me.
I am sorry, but I do not know anything.
But I really, really know nothing!
I see, I am sorry to hear that.
If this girl knows who Sailor Moon is,
she is certain to contact her somehow.
Oh, my, what a foolish man.
Has he fallen in love with a human girl?
You three, I believe you have heard everything you need to know.
We do not want to get hurt by making any ill-planned moves.
We will take that girl as a hostage and lure him out.
How can I find out where Sailor Moon is?
Who in the world is calling me in the middle of night?
Usagi, I am sorry for calling you so late.
I just thought you are the only one I could talk to.
Mr. Sanjoin... Mr. Sanjoin is looking for Sailor Moon.
Mr. Sanjoin is in trouble, but I cannot do anything for him.
What is wrong with Mr. Sanjoin?
I am sorry for making such a weird call to you in the middle of night.
I feel calmer now after talking to you, Usagi.
I will bet Nephrite is closing in on Naru!
Hey, I am not a cat!
It is must be the work of a monster!
You have finally revealed yourself, Sailor Moon!
The true identity of Sailor Moon is Usagi Tsukino.
Do not tell anybody that I am Sailor Moon!
There is no need for you to hide it anymore.
Do not worry you are going to die here!
I do not want to die!
Defeat is not befitting of the beautiful Sailor Moon.
We shall conclude this fight another time.
Sailor Moon, I know who you are now!
I will be able to attack you at any time now!
Do not give up just because he knows who you are now.
I need to contact the sailor warriors!
Hand over the Black Crystal in exchange for the girl?
Who cares what happens to that girl?!
Will he really come for this human?
Well, if he does not show up, we will just kill the girl.
I will never hand over the Black Crystal to you guys!
You do not need to thank me.
I do not even really understand why I rescued you.
And I have kept deceiving you for a long time.
I may continue to lie to you, even after this.
If you will just stay close to me,
I do not mind being lied to.
You were hurt because of me!
You were hurt because of me!
It would be bad if those scary people come back, so come this way.
there is a place that serves really good chocolate parfaits.
Sometimes we lie with kind intentions, too.
I always thought it would be nice to go to there one day
and have a chocolate parfait with you.
It is a little dream of mine.
Do you think I am lying?
Oh, come to think of it,
does the evil organization give you Sundays off, too?
Those thorns will keep sucking your energy until you die!
What a miserable way to die.
If you do not want us to kill the girl, hand over the Black Crystal!
Do you think you can pull them out with the strength of a human?
Mr. Nephrite, please do not die!
Damn it, I will take care of both of them at once!
The Black Crystal is mine now.
You should be happy to able to die with the girl you love.
You guys make sure to have plenty of fun with them.
You are really mean, trying to interfere with two people in love!
In the name of the moon, I will punish you!
Stand under a cold waterfall and reflect on your conduct!
In the name of Mars, I will chastise you!
We will take care of you guys first!
It looks like your identity may remain a secret.
I do not think we will get to eat a chocolate parfait together.
I have ended up lying to you to the very end.
I am glad I met you.
You said we would eat a chocolate parfait together!
Yume no naka futari de ita yo ne
Tomodachi no toki ni wa ki ni sezu
Anata dake ki ni naru shunkan ga atta no
Motto kirei ni i am about to sugu naritai
Koi suru to nanika ga kawaru ne
Dakishimeta tokimeki sono mama kono omoi tsutaetai
